                  <h2 class="featured-story__title">
                    Azerbaijan National Team Wins Gold at ISSF World Cup
                  </h2>

                  <p class="featured-story__excerpt">
                    Azerbaijani athletes delivered outstanding performances
                    during the ISSF World Cup finals, securing multiple medals
                    across rifle and pistol disciplines.
