                  <h2 class="featured-story__title">
                    Official meeting between ISSF officials and Azerbaijani
                    representatives in Baku
                  </h2>

                  <p class="featured-story__excerpt">
                    ISSF President Luciano Rossi and General Secretary
                    Alessandro Nicotra di San Giacomo met the Minister of the
                    Interior & President of the Azerbaijan Shooting Federation
                    Vilayat Eyvazov and Deputy Minister of the Interior Ismat
                    Alijev ahead of the ISSF World Cup in Baku.
                  </p>

                  <a href="article-01/" class="featured-story__link-btn"
